// =============================================================================
// kernel/core/boot_helpers.salt — Boot Sequence (extracted from main.salt)
// =============================================================================
// Contains functions previously in main.salt that were extracted to keep
// each file under 500 lines. All functions use @no_mangle for direct
// linker-level cross-module calls (same pattern as the rest of the kernel).

